products.title: Dell i7 8gb
products.description:
6th Generation Intel Core i7-6500U Dual-Core Processor 2.5 GHz (max 
boost speed up to 3.1GHz) 4MB L3 Cache, 8GB DDR4 1600 MHz, 1TB 5400 RPM 
HDD15.6 in Full HD LED-backlit touchscreen with Truelife (1920 x 1080), 
10-finger multi-touch support, Intel HD Graphics 520 with shared 
graphics memory

products.title: Iphone 6 32gb
products.description:
It comes with 1GB of RAM. The phone packs 16GB of internal storage 
cannot be expanded. As far as the cameras are concerned, the Apple 
iPhone 6 packs a 8-megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 
1.2-megapixel front shooter for selfies.
